summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5623 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 11, First Plat of West Seattle, being the alley between California Avenue and 42nd Avenue Southwest, from West Seattle Street to West Atlantic Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 74197, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
